OL,3,CTributes paid to 'Sir Fab' - the
OL,4,CLieutenant Governor who was full of fun
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to Guernsey's
OL,7,Fformer Lieutenant Governor, Sir Fabian
OL,8,FMalbon, who is being remembered as a
OL,9,F"good sport" and "full of fun" by
OL,10,Fthose who knew him best.
OL,12,FThe Royal Navy Officer - who was
OL,13,Faffectionately known as 'Sir Fab' by
OL,14,Fmany on the island - served as
OL,15,FLieutenant Governor from 2005 to 2011.
OL,17,FHe died at the age of 79 on Saturday
OL,18,F(January 17th).
